YAY! today was the first day of band camp.We did the usual uniform fitting.I've gained a lot of weight being lazy over the summer, and the band moms (that i dont recognize =[) dont believe me when i say ill lose ALL of it maybe plus some after band camp or such.thus leaving me with a huge uniform hahaha.We got to play "My Favorite things" today.ya know like from The sound of Music?i really should watch that movie because i dont think ive seen it.IT WAS AWESOME AND JAZZY! hahaha. Oh and in that slow song, i forget the name, sax has a solo well more like a quartet.but still very cool.oh and if harlAn (haha) doesnt come to band camp again, i may have a chance at landin the part (because of course we have to try out for them).Oh and LOVE mr. cobb (i mean as much as i know of him hahaha, well good first impression) lets pray he stays like my first impression of him.oh and a MUCH MUCH MUCH MUCH better player than mrs. dix. man he can play.loud with tone.and i was right in front of him so i got the lot of it.Oh and my whole section are freshmen currently (i only say my section because im the oldest one there haha) i hope qwentin comes to band camp , but not harlin because i want that solo HAHAHAHA.but hey qwentin may just step up there and beat me out.or a freshmen but probably not because Lydia is playing 2nd part, and considering bari.Oh cameron and dillon have grills, dallas has an afro, and donica made field commander again.So i need to practice because i absolutely love the jazz show.but i cant think of anythign else to write, but today was awesome.but i still need to finish The once and Future King, but its a pretty interesting summer assignment.And i need to start Harry Potter.Oh and I wore my Mrs. Nash button and the Freshman Tuba Player knew who it was.sweet.oh and ive said sweet almost too many times today and i tackled everyone i saw today.yay band =]and dude the chipper star has has musical notes around it
